<h1 class="title">ProblemsWithHemisphereMixing</h1>
<p>
Hemisphere mixing works well, but is a bit ad hoc &#x2013; requires a to metric to be defined between hemispheres &#x2013; and is cumbersome to use &#x2013; it scales as O(N<sup>2</sup>) because of a nested loop over events.
